TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> What gem are you talking about?
Make you beautiful? What do you mean?
I have something that might make you beautiful again.
Text: 널 다시 아름답게 만들 수 있는 게 있어.

TextEng: I'm looking for some missing druids.
I have other things I need to do.
Make you purty? What you mean?
Me look for missin' folk.
Me have somethin' to make you purty, yuh?
Text: 나 너 예뻐지게 만들어줄 거 있어, 알지?

TextEng: Uh, yuh, me go now.
No, a potion of nymph's tears.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> No, a magic mirror. Anyone who peers into it is made beautiful.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 아니, 마법 거울이야. 들여다보는 사람을 누구나 아름답게 만들어줘.

TextEng: Sorry, I was mistaken, Setara.
No, me have potion of purtiness for you.
Text: 아니, 나 너 예뻐지게 해주는 물약 있어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> No, me have magic mirror. It make you purty, see?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 아니, 나 마법 거울 있어. 그게 너 예쁘게 만들어줘, 알지?

TextEng: Uh, me goof up. Sorry.
Setara, you had mentioned a gem.
Setara, I'm still looking for those druids.
All right, take care of yourself.
Uh, you talk 'bout gem...
Uh, me still look for missin' folk.
Text: 어, 나 아직도 잃어버린 사람들 찾고 있어.

TextEng: Me go if that okay.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Shed a tear? What do you mean?
